---
// ArchiveCTA.astro - Rebuilt with native Tailwind
---

<section class="relative bg-black py-16 md:py-24 overflow-hidden w-full">
    {/* Top SVG Wave Divider */}
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full overflow-hidden leading-none" style="height: 60px;">
        <svg class="relative block w-full h-full" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1000 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path class="fill-[#ffffcc]" d="M421.9,6.5c22.6-2.5,51.5,0.4,75.5,5.3c23.6,4.9,70.9,23.5,100.5,35.7c75.8,32.2,133.7,44.5,192.6,49.7c23.6,2.1,48.7,3.5,103.4-2.5c54.7-6,106.2-25.6,106.2-25.6V0H0v30.3c0,0,72,32.6,158.4,30.5c39.2-0.7,92.8-6.7,134-22.4c21.2-8.1,52.2-18.2,79.7-24.2C399.3,7.9,411.6,7.5,421.9,6.5z"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 pt-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
            
            {/* Left Content */}
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
                <h4 class="text-[#f2cf19] font-bold text-lg md:text-xl uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Liên Hệ Tư Vấn Mua Sỉ Lẻ</h4>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-8">
                    Chúng tôi có chính sách hệ thống phân phối cho khách hàng sỉ
                </h2>
                
                <a href="https://zalo.me/0963447890" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#f2cf19] hover:bg-yellow-500 text-black font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
                    <span class="mr-2">Liên Hệ Zalo</span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            {/* Right Image */}
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-0">
                <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500">
                    <img 
                        src="https://media.hethongbiatuoi.com/he-thong-bia-thap-di-den-cac-quan-an-tren-khap-noi.webp" 
                        alt="Hệ thống bia tháp đi đến các tiệm tạp hóa toàn quốc" 
                        class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>